#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Psychiclysm"
msgstr "心靈災變"

#. ~ Description for Psychiclysm
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adapts some Magiclysm features for psychic phenomena.  Changes nether "
"monsters fear attacks to an incremental effect.  Gives many monsters psi-"
"attacks.  Adds mesmerism options to NPC dialog.  Psychic Duels with other "
"mentalists."
msgstr ""
"將一些魔法災變特性適配於心靈現象。將下界怪物的恐懼攻擊改為漸進效果。賦予許多怪物心靈攻擊能力。在NPC對話中添加催眠選項。與其他心靈能力者進行心靈決鬥。"

