#: .\skills.json
msgid "psychology"
msgstr "心理學"

#. ~ Description for psychology
#: .\skills.json
msgid ""
"Your skill in understanding other people.  Covers speaking ability, such as "
"boasting, flattery, threats, persuasion, lies, and other facets of "
"interpersonal communication.  Works best in conjunction with a high level of"
" intelligence."
msgstr "你理解他人的技能。涵蓋說話能力，如吹噓、奉承、威脅、說服、撒謊以及其他人際溝通方面。與高智力水平結合時效果最佳。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Feel the power."
msgstr "感受這股力量。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "This will be over soon."
msgstr "這一切很快就會結束。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Your mind is weak."
msgstr "你的意志很薄弱。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Nothing can stop me."
msgstr "沒有什麼能阻止我。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Give up.  Your battle is hopeless."
msgstr "放棄吧。你的戰鬥毫無希望。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Your mind is cracking."
msgstr "你的意志正在崩潰。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "This is the end for you."
msgstr "你的末日到了。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Cease your struggling."
msgstr "停止你的掙扎。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "My victory is near."
msgstr "我的勝利近在咫尺。"

#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Soon!"
msgstr "快了！"
